posting_body: ['Fountain Plaza (CA)', '190 ryland Street, San Jose, CA, 95110', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'FOUNTAIN PLAZA IN SAN JOSE RADIATES STYLE AND SOPHISTICATION', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 748 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'From the inside out – right in the center of Silicon Valley.', 'Vibrant decor and Spanish-influenced design lend a traditional vibe, while tech-savvy details and beautiful landscaping keeps things modern and always relaxed.', 'Work, connect, play and get inspired at Fountain Plaza.', '**Greystar California, Inc., Broker License #01525765**Please consult the community leasing office to determine applicable licensed company.', 'Features', '- Personal Balconies*', '- Maple, Raised-Panel Kitchen Cabinets', '- Kitchen Islands*', '- Loft-Style Floor Plans*', '- Built-In Desks*', '- Spiral Staircases*', '- Full-Size Washers and Dryers', '- Wired for Ceiling Fans in Bedrooms and Living Room*', '- Wired for Alarm System', '- Oversized Closets*', '- Elevator*', '- Garden-Style Soaking Tubs*', 'Community Amenities', '- Furnished Units Available*', '- Resident Clubhouse', '- Near Public Transportation', '- See Sales Associate for Details.', '- Minutes from Downtown San Jose', '- Business Center', '- Close to Shopping and Fine Dining', '- Resort-Style Pool', '- We Love Pets!*', '- Relaxing Spa', '- Conference Room', '- Garage or Covered Parking*', '- 24/7 Complete Fitness Center', '- Easy Access to Highways 87, 280, 101 and 880', '- Additional Storage Available', '- Gated Community', '- Close to Hiking and Biking Trails', '*Restrictions Apply.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Income Requirements:', '3x the amount of rent', 'gse25lc8ZUT']
